15 WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
16 Statutes, the Oklahoma State Legislature shall adopt a separate
17 joint resolution to approve or disapprove major rules.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
19 AND THE SENATE OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
20 SECTION 1. The Legislature hereby approves the following
21 proposed major rule changes submitted by the Oklahoma Medical
22 Marijuana Authority on or before February 1, 2026: OAC 442:10-1-9;
23 442:10-1-9.1; 442:10-2-1; 442:10-2-2; 442:10-2-4; 442:10-2-6;
24 442:10-3-1; 442:10-3-6; 442:10-4-1; 442:10-4-4; 442:10-4-5; 442:10-
